---
# var-naming[no-role-prefix] is skipped because the collection's role variables
# (home_user, krew_plugins, kubectl_version, ...) are user-facing override knobs.
# Renaming them to e.g. setup_shell_home_user would be a breaking change for
# existing consumers and would not improve clarity in practice.
skip_list:
  - var-naming[no-role-prefix]
